parameters.name: UT
parameters.description: Universal Time given in PDS format: yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sss.

parameters.name: E100HZMX
parameters.description:
Maximum wave amplitude per root Hertz per 24 
  second interval, measured at 100 Hz.  At a particular frequency the wave    
  electric field amplitude (V/M) is measured over the bandwidth of the filter 
  (30% for OEFD).  The square root of the bandwidth is incorporated in order  
  to compare measurements made with this instrument with other wave           
  measurements, which may have different bandwidths.
